					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Only problem with argv is that it's not Unicode on Windows.  On Linux, all 8-bit strings are UTF-8, so things just work.  But not on Windows, where 8-bit strings are localized to whatever the system locale is set to.  On Windows, you need to call GetCommandLineW to get the Unicode version of the command line.</div>

					
